                <tr>
                    <td>User Authentication</td>
                    <td>Users can create accounts and log in to access personalized features.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Search Functionality</td>
                    <td>Users can search for cars, auctions, or services within the platform.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Notification System</td>
                    <td>The application will inform users about updates on their auctions, maintenance requests, and
                        marketplace activities.
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>User Profiles</td>
                    <td>Users can create and manage personal profiles to store their preferences and history.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Security</td>
                    <td>The application will implement robust security measures to protect user data and transactions.
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Customer Support</td>
                    <td>Users can reach out for assistance or to report issues through a built-in customer support
                        feature.
                    </td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Specific Features</h2>
            <table class="table-bordered">
