                    <td> Provision of maintenance services requests, scheduling, a location to meet and type of service
                        required and license plate number.
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Marketplace</td>
                    <td> A platform for selling cars by the users, approved by the admins for publication.</td>

                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Auction</td>
                    <td> Facilitating live bidding for car auctions, managed by the admins.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Car Parts Provision</td>
                    <td> Members can request car parts based on their car license number.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Car Rentals</td>
                    <td> Offering car rental services.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Car Showrooms</td>
                    <td> Car showrooms can also register and provide cars for sale or rental.</td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
