        </section>
        <section>
            <p>
                Please note that the platform will support multiple payment methods, including Credit Cards, Apple Pay,
                and Google Pay. The application will also support multilingual interfaces, initially available in two
                languages, and will have seamless integration with its mobile applications to ensure a consistent user
                experience across platforms.
            </p>
